      "description": "The Invesco QQQ Hedged Advantage ETF (QQHG) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in large cap equity. The fund seeks to provide capital appreciation through an actively managed portfolio that holds Nasdaq-100 stocks. The fund employs an options overlay strategy to partially hedge downside risk. QQHG was launched on May 7, 2025 and is issued by Invesco.",
